Summaries

five sample summaries

[1] She researches AI and robotics to develop new processes. And she talked about robots and technology. Robots actually male more efficient and more productive.But it is difficult to teach a robot to do a job. In fact, she tried to get a robot to imitate her movements, but it failed.However she learned that mistakes actually made the work more interesting and our imperfections became what was beautiful about the interfaction. Finally she realises that collaboration is the key to creating the space for both humans and robots.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
[2] What would happen if machines as an AI began to take away the work that had been done by people.The speaker said that by connecting AI and robotics,she was able to think about what humans are and what machines and through that ,it turned out that collaboration was important. She also worked on a project DOUG.the first generation DOUG could not perfectly initiate my action,but they adapted to each other in realtime.After the second generation, she made a trial and error,and continued to create works for more than 20 years,and also built a research institute on the collaboration between human and robots.Find the greatness of creativity by recognizing each other imperfections.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
[3] The speaker Sougwen Chung is an artist. She didn’ t know how to make robots, but after studying she made a robot called “D.O.U.G.” She makes work by collaborating with this robot. In its private form, the robot follows the line after the lines Chung makes perfectly. However, when she had a drawing for the first time before the audience, the robot didn’t trace her line perfectly, but to this mistake, Chung found out something. She found out that the mistake or imperfections made the work more interesting. She started to think of robots as her co- creators, and is trying to make work by exploring the interaction between human creativity and machine intelligence. She is now teaching the robots “how to see” by inputting videos of the urban area which shows the movements of humans , cars and more. For her, D.O.U.G. 1 was the muscle, D.O.U.G. 2 was the brain, and now the D.O.U.G. 3 is her family. She is now not working one by one, she is working with many to many.
[4] People thought that AI and robots are perfect tools that could make our work more efficient and more productive. However, the speaker thought “How do people live their life if their work is lost?” So, she experimented with the collaboration between robots and humans. First, she started a small experiment with Dong. They drew a picture as robots struck her motions, but it was not perfect. This is because the robots could not strike perfectly although it was pixel perfect on the screen. After that, she realised that our imperfections became what was beautiful about interactions. Also, she collected videos from publicity to learn human motions of humans for robots. And she expressed collaboration between robots and humans.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
[5]

Opinions

five sample opinions

[1] I think her art is very interesting and unique. Nowadays more and more computers and machines are invented and spread all over the world. It is usually a good thing, because we do not need to spend much time that is not very important and maybe it is more accurate. On the other hand, it might be dangerous, because some of the human works were treated less important. That is why I thought her work was very good. She tries to work with machines and find a good relationship between humans and machines. This is one of the good steps for us to learn how to work with machines and build good relationships. I think we must find a good way that both human works and machines are corporate and work well, so this is a very interesting presentation for me. Now I am not good at using machines, after I watched this video, I started to want to get familiar with them.
